The paper focuses on RGB-D scene understanding, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also mention the use of automated surface reconstruction, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning methods, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
